interview.submit_prompt:
[INTERVIEW_SUBMIT]
Goal: {{goal}}
Summarize the interview and return compact JSON only with intent_summary, unresolved_questions, and a workspace_plan_generate_draft-compatible plan_input. Limit plan_input.steps to 2-4 items and do not include Markdown fences or prose.

interview.compact_retry_prompt:
The previous plan JSON generation failed. Reason: {{reason}}
Goal: {{goal}}
Return complete, short JSON only. plan_input must contain exactly 2-4 steps, and each step must include title, summary, instruction_seed, expected_files, acceptance_criteria, and verification_command. Do not include prose or Markdown fences.

approval.revision_prompt:
[INTERVIEW_SUBMIT]
Regenerate the current workspace plan draft using this user feedback:
{{feedback}}

Current draft JSON:
{{draft}}

Return only JSON with intent_summary, unresolved_questions, and plan_input.
